Scope of this license

This MIT license applies to the files authored as part of this repository:
the compose files (base.yaml, addons.yaml, graphdb.yaml, le-bootstrap.yaml),
the nginx configuration under files/nginx/, the Console landing page under
files/console/, the helper scripts under scripts/, the Terraform module under
infra/terraform/, and the Markdown documentation at the repo root and under
infra/.

It does NOT grant any license or warranty covering:

- The proprietary Ontotext / Graphwise product binaries and container images
  that the compose files pull at runtime (PoolParty, GraphDB, GraphDB
  Enterprise Edition, UnifiedViews, ADF, Semantic Workbench, GraphViews).
  Those are governed by separate commercial license agreements between the
  user and Graphwise. Obtain them from Graphwise directly
  (https://graphwise.ai/).
- The third-party open-source images the stack depends on (Keycloak, nginx,
  Elasticsearch, Eclipse RDF4J, podman, Debian, and others). Each ships
  under its own upstream license — typically Apache 2.0, BSD, or similar —
  and those upstream terms apply when those images are pulled and run.
- Any trademarks or service marks of Graphwise, Ontotext, or any third-party
  vendor whose software is used by the stack.

The fact that this repository is publicly visible on GitHub does not grant
any license to the Graphwise product suite or to any vendor image it
depends on.

