No support

This repository is a reference guide published primarily for internal use
by Graphwise field presales engineers. It is made public for convenience and
community reference. No support, uptime guarantee, or bug-fix commitment is
offered. Graphwise presales engineers may or may not respond to issues or
pull requests, at their discretion. For production deployments or paid
support, engage Graphwise's professional services organization directly.
